ih|QJ432 KQ5432 - K2|n#|7|at|
^b@2
|ht|p|at|^^^g@2Eg: you as RESPONDER hold this hand and Declarer opens 1@s.

Now 4 @d is Exclusion Beta and we'll find out if Partner has enough controls OUTSIDE Diamonds for us to make a Small or Grand Slam.

^b@2If Partner has 0-4 Controls  outside Diamonds, then any slam is a dead duck, but if 5 or 6 we can bid a small slam and the magic 7 will mean a Grand is on the cards.|
